  rulesTitle: Seed Chess Rules
  rulesText: "The board starts with only two Kings.\n\nSelect your King, then tap
    a seed button to plant a piece seed on an adjacent empty square.\n\nGrowth turns:\n 
    Pawn: 1  |  Knight: 3  |  Bishop: 3\n  Rook: 5  |  Queen: 9\n\nSeeds are passable
    and cannot be captured.\nWhen a seed's timer reaches 0 it hatches into the real
    piece.\n\nCheckmate or stalemate ends the game."
